casebody.data:
No. 13,

Original.

Missouri et al. v. Davey et al. John M. Dalton, Attorney General of Missouri, and Robert L. Ryder for plaintiffs. Latham Castle, Attorney General of Illinois, and William C. Wines, Assistant Attorney General, for Streeper, and Schaefer O’Neill for Struif et al., defendants.

The motion for leave to file bill of complaint is denied. Illinois v. Wisconsin, 333 U. S. 879; Louisiana v. Cummins, 314 U. S. 580; and Massachusetts v. Missouri, 308 U. S. 1, 18-20.
